org.stekikun.dolmen.common

Class Sets

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.stekikun.dolmen.common.Sets

  • public abstract class Sets
extends Object
    This class contains various utility methods about Sets. The various operations like union(Set, Set) and so on assume an immutable use of the sets used as parameters, since they are optimized to return one of the input sets instead of new sets when possible. I wished I had Guava available!
    Author:
    St√©phane Lescuyer
